Paula Winslowe https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paula_Winslowe 0 Paula Winslowe (born Winifred Reyleche; March 23, 1910 – March 6, 1996), sometimes credited as Paula Winslow, was a radio and television actress and is known for her role as Bambi's mother in the 1942 movie Bambi.
